    mainHeader: `Hottest Hair Trends for 2023`,
    subHeader: "",
    contentHeader: `Hottest Hair Trends for 2023`,
    content:
      "<p class='first'>As we move into 2023, it's time to take a look at the top hairstyle trends that are set to take the beauty world by storm. From bold cuts to vibrant colours, these are the looks that you can expect to see on the heads of trendsetters and fashionistas in the coming year.</p><h2>1.	Choppy Pixie Cut</h2><div><img src='/images/hottestHair-1.jpg' class='block m-auto  md:pt-5 object-contain max-w-[250px]' /><p class='text-center text-sm py-1 max-w-[700px] m-auto'>Image source:<a href='https://www.pinterest.co.uk/pin/170292429651019410/'>pinterest.co</a></p></div><p>The choppy pixie cut is set to be a popular choice for those looking to make a bold statement with their hair. This look involves choppy layers and textured fringe, and is perfect for those with fine or straight hair.</p><p></p><h2>2.	Blunt Bob</h2><div><img src='/images/hottestHair-2.jpg' class='block m-auto  md:pt-5 object-contain max-w-[250px]' /><p class='text-center text-sm py-1 max-w-[700px] m-auto'>Image source:<a href='https://www.pinterest.co.uk/pin/1120340844777948947/'>pinterest.co</a></p></div><p>The blunt bob is a classic hairstyle that is set to make a big comeback in 2023. This look involves a sharp, straight cut that falls just below the chin, and is perfect for those with thick, straight hair.</p><h2>3.	Curtain Bangs</h2><div><img src='/images/hottestHair-3.jpg' class='block m-auto  md:pt-5 object-contain max-w-[250px]' /><p class='text-center text-sm py-1 max-w-[700px] m-auto'>Image source:<a href='https://www.pinterest.co.uk/pin/wednesday--113645590589225499/'>pinterest.co</a></p></div><p>Curtain bangs are a versatile and low-maintenance option for those looking to switch up their look. This style involves long, side-swept bangs that frame the face, and is perfect for those with wavy or curly hair.</p><h2>4.	Bold Hair Colours</h2><div><img src='/images/hottestHair-4.jpg' class='block m-auto  md:pt-5 object-contain max-w-[250px]' /><p class='text-center text-sm py-1 max-w-[700px] m-auto'>Image source:<a href='https://www.pinterest.co.uk/pin/815925657494999588/'>pinterest.co</a></p></div><p>Bold hair colours are set to be all the rage in 2023, with bright, eye-catching shades taking centre stage. From vibrant pinks and purples to bold blues and greens, there's a colour out there to suit every taste.</p><h2>5.	Updos with a Twist</h2><div><img src='/images/hottestHair-5.jpg' class='block m-auto  md:pt-5 object-contain max-w-[250px]' /><p class='text-center text-sm py-1 max-w-[700px] m-auto'>Image source:<a href='https://www.pinterest.co.uk/pin/637048309804402279/'>pinterest.co</a></p></div><p>Updos are set to be a popular choice for those looking to add a touch of glamour to their look. In 2023, expect to see updos with a twist, such as braids or twists incorporated into the style for a unique and eye-catching look.</p><p>So, 2023 is set to be an exciting year for hair trends, with a range of bold and eye-catching looks taking centre stage. Whether you're looking to make a dramatic change with a choppy pixie cut or simply want to switch up your look with a bold hair colour, there's a style out there to suit every taste. So why not take the plunge and try out a new look for the new year?</p>",
